%% hook-utils getActivePhaseFromWorkflowState state machine (post-fix)

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> ReadTaskIndex: hook invoked
    ReadTaskIndex --> PhaseResolved: active entry found
    ReadTaskIndex --> ScanWorkflows: no entry in task-index
    ScanWorkflows --> TryJson: workflow-state.json exists
    ScanWorkflows --> TryToon: workflow-state.toon exists
    ScanWorkflows --> NoActive: neither file present
    TryJson --> PhaseResolved: phase key present and not completed
    TryJson --> TryToon: json missing phase
    TryToon --> PhaseResolved: phase line extracted (first 64KB)
    TryToon --> NoActive: no phase line
    PhaseResolved --> AllowWrite: phase is active
    PhaseResolved --> NoActive: phase is completed or idle
    NoActive --> BlockWrite
    AllowWrite --> [*]
    BlockWrite --> [*]

%% ## decisions
%% - D-001: TOON読み取りはJSON読み取りの後続フォールバックとして動作
%% - D-002: phase値が completed または idle の場合は NoActive 扱い
%% - D-003: TOON読み取りは先頭64KB制限でDoSリスクを低減
%% - D-004: TaskIndex経路とWorkflowState経路の両方を保持し互換維持
%% - D-005: 既存シグネチャ変更なし、内部分岐の追加のみ
